He's the one who got me to come.

1049
01:11:57,791 --> 01:12:00,055
- Twin screenwriters?
- Yeah.

1050
01:12:00,227 --> 01:12:04,186
Well, Julius and Philip Epstein...

1051
01:12:04,364 --> 01:12:07,128
...who wrote Casablanca...

1052
01:12:07,300 --> 01:12:10,235
